<topic id="yaml-outline-view">
  <title>YAML Outline View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>YAML documents<indexterm>Outline view</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_uvf_cgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view for YAML documents displays the
      list of all the components of the document you are editing in a hierarchical (tree-like)
      representation. It is synchronized with the main editor so you can use the view to navigate to
      specific parts of the document and move or delete components. By default, it is displayed on
      the left side of the editor. <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
    <p id="p_vvf_cgk_54b">
      <fig id="fig_wvf_cgk_54b">
        <title>YAML Outline View</title>
        <image href="../img/yaml-outline.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <section id="outline_view_features">
      <title>Outline View Features</title>
      <p id="p_zvf_cgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view allows you to:<ul id="ul_awf_cgk_54b">
          <li id="li_bwf_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Quickly navigate through the document by selecting nodes in the
              <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> tree.</li>
          <li id="li_cwf_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Move elements by dragging them to a new position in the tree structure.</li>
          <li id="li_dwf_cgk_54b" irina="irina">Highlight elements in the editor area. It is synchronized with the editor area, so
            when you make a selection in the editor area, the corresponding nodes are highlighted in
            the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view, and vice versa.</li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
    <section id="outline_view_interface">
      <title>Outline View Interface</title>
      <p id="p_fwf_cgk_54b">By default, it is displayed on the left side of the editor. <ph
          conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"/></p>
      <p conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/outliner-filter-box" id="p_gwf_cgk_54b"/>
      <p id="p_hwf_cgk_54b">It also includes a <ph product="author developer editor json"
              ><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png"/>Settings</uicontrol> menu</ph><ph
          product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"><uicontrol>View
          menu</uicontrol></ph> in the top-right corner that presents the following options to help
        you filter the view even further.</p>
      <p id="p_iwf_cgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_jwf_cgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="filter-returns-exact-dlentry">
            <dt><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>The text filter of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact
              matches.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_kwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CaretUpdateOff16.png" id="image_km1_vft_tr"
                />Selection update on cursor move</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Controls the synchronization between <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view and source
              document. The selection in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view can be synchronized
              with the cursor moves or the changes in the editor. Selecting one of the components
              from the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view also selects the corresponding item in
              the source document.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_lwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Flat16.png" placement="inline"/>Flat presentation
                mode of the filtered results</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>When active, the application flattens the filtered result elements to a single
              level.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="contextual_menu_actions">
      <title>Contextual Menu Actions</title>
      <p id="p_swf_cgk_54b">The following actions are available in the contextual menu of the YAML
          <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view:</p>
      <p id="p_twf_cgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_uwf_cgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="dlentry_vwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Cut16.png" id="image_u1f_hz1_5r"
              />Cut</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Cuts the currently selected component.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_wwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_x2z_mst_tr"
              />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Copies the currently selected component.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_xwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Paste16.png" id="image_ms5_gqt_tr"
              />Paste</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Pastes the copied component.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_ywf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" placement="inline"
                  id="image_b41_5jg_ks"/>Delete</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Deletes the currently selected component.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_zwf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol product="developer editor json"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                  placement="inline" id="image_lny_prd_cs"/>Expand More</uicontrol><uicontrol
                product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                  placement="inline" id="image_ywc_f1j_cs"/>Expand All</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Expands the structure of a component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol>
              view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_axf_cgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/CollapseAll16.png" id="image_yl1_r3t_tr"/>Collapse
                All</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Collapses the structure of all the component in the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol>
              view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
